column5: What would be a good channel for the hand held radios for tomorrow?  How about channel #3?  See you there.
I am going to be fishing by myself and i will need someone to talk to.
I always like  talking to myself.That way I know were both right.LOL
And don't forget the intelligent answers you get to your questions
I always keep 6 on Simcoe,but tomorrow 3 it is....TC and see ya there ....Chuck....

Hey Glen what colour will you have on? I'll be wearing mostly black (I know that may not help much) no radio, no portable hut, just looking down the hole and staring at the screen. I don't know if I'll be driving out on to the ice or not, but if I do I'll have the blue CRV.
